definitions.definition: The act of rising out of a fluid , or coming forth from envelopment or concealment , or of rising into view; appearance .

subdefinitions.definition: The arising of emergent structure in complex systems.

definitions.definition: An outgrowth from the surface, such as a prickle or wart, differing from hairs in arising from more than the superficial cells, and from spines in arising from a few layers only.

main_definition: The act of rising out of a fluid , or coming forth from envelopment or concealment , or of rising into view; appearance .
